data.description: Upon Entry, this home boasts a GRAND foyer fit for royalty. In-Law suite with access to a full bath on first floor. Our exclusive ORB door hardware and lighting package along w/SS appliances. Rustic Mantel electric FP w/stone surround, custom cabinetry in all baths and Kitchen. Custom 3ft island with 7ft granite top. PRIVATE homesite w/ tree buffer in back yard. Only 10 miles from FT Campbell,5 mins to Publix, w/access from Tinytown or the 101.
